## Chat Template Handler Implementation in llama.cpp

I've thoroughly analyzed the chat template handler system in llama.cpp. Here's a comprehensive overview:

### Architecture Overview

The chat template system is located in:
- **Header**: `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775465022763-8szz5u/common/chat.h`
